original: Ågren, Edvin Teofil, fd. distriktsveterinär, Finspång, f. 1/4/84 i Karlskrona av folkskoll. F. A. A. o. Bengta Olsson. G. 17 m. Rut Nygren. — Farm. kand. 07, veter. 16. Distriveter. i Öje-byn 16, i Mörsil 22, i Finspång 28-47, pens.
translated: Ågren, Edvin Teofil, former district veterinarian, Finspång, born April 1, 1884 in Karlskrona, son of F.A.A. and Bengta Olsson. Married on the 17th of an unknown month to Rut Nygren. - Bachelor of Pharmacy in 1907, veterinarian in 1916. District veterinarian in Öje-byn from 1916, in Mörsil from 1922, in Finspång from 1928-1947, retired.
